'''葡萄糖淀粉酶'''（glucoamylase）又称'''γ-淀粉酶'''（gamma-amylase）、'''淀粉葡糖苷酶'''（amyloglucosidase，AMG），全名'''葡聚糖 1,4-α-葡糖苷酶'''，是一種[[酸性|酸性]]的單鏈外切型[[糖苷|糖苷]][[水解酶|水解酶]]，不僅能催化[[澱粉|澱粉]]水解為[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]，還能從澱粉糖鏈的非還原末端 (即不可以形成[[半縮醛|半縮醛]]的[[羥基|羥基]]) 切下葡萄糖[[分子|分子]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sauer |first1=J |last2=Sigurskjold |first2=BW |last3=Christensen |first3=U |last4=Frandsen |first4=TP |last5=Mirgorodskaya |first5=E |last6=Harrison |first6=M |last7=Roepstorff |first7=P |last8=Svensson |first8=B |title=Glucoamylase: structure/function relationships, and protein engineering. |journal=Biochimica et biophysica acta |date=2000-12-29 |volume=1543 |issue=2 |pages=275-293 |doi=10.1016/s0167-4838(00)00232-6 |pmid=11150611 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11150611-glucoamylase-structurefunction-relationships-and-protein-engineering/ |accessdate=2019-12-24}}</ref>。γ-淀粉酶存在于动物（[[小肠|小肠]]）、微生物中。

葡萄糖澱粉酶目前已在食品、醫藥和[[發酵|發酵]]工業等領域得到廣泛的應用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nguyen |first1=Quang D |last2=Rezessy-Szabó |first2=Judit M |last3=Claeyssens |first3=Marc |last4=Stals |first4=Ingeborg |last5=Hoschke |first5=Ágoston |title=Purification and characterisation of amylolytic enzymes from thermophilic fungus Thermomyces lanuginosus strain ATCC 34626 |journal=Enzyme and Microbial Technology |date=2002-08 |volume=31 |issue=3 |pages=345–352 |doi=10.1016/S0141-0229(02)00128-X |accessdate=2019-12-24}}</ref><ref name=a>{{cite journal |last1=Pandey |first1=A |last2=Nigam |first2=P |last3=Soccol |first3=CR |last4=Soccol |first4=VT |last5=Singh |first5=D |last6=Mohan |first6=R |title=Advances in microbial amylases. |journal=Biotechnology and applied biochemistry |date=2000-04 |volume=31 |issue=2 |pages=135-52 |doi=10.1042/ba19990073 |pmid=10744959 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10744959-advances-in-microbial-amylases/ |accessdate=2019-12-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kumar |first1=P |last2=Satyanarayana |first2=T |title=Microbial glucoamylases: characteristics and applications. |journal=Critical reviews in biotechnology |date=2009 |volume=29 |issue=3 |pages=225-55 |doi=10.1080/07388550903136076 |pmid=19708824 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19708824-microbial-glucoamylases-characteristics-and-applications/ |accessdate=2019-12-24}}</ref>。[[工業|工業]]上應用的葡萄糖澱粉酶主要來自於[[麴黴屬|麴黴屬]]及[[根黴|根黴屬]]，極少來自於[[鐮孢菌屬|鐮孢菌屬]]。例如半裸鐮刀菌 (Fusarium Semitectum) <ref name=b>{{cite journal |last1=. |first1=Altaf Hussain |last2=. |first2=Zafar Iqbal Khan |last3=. |first3=Dr. Ejaz Rasul |title=Isolation and Screening of Amylolytic and Pectinolytic Fungi from Soil |journal=Pakistan Journal of Biological Sciences |date=1999-03-01 |volume=2 |issue=3 |pages=974–975 |doi=10.3923/pjbs.1999.974.975 |accessdate=2019-12-24}}</ref>、[[尖孢鐮刀菌|尖孢鐮刀菌]]<ref name=b/>、{{le|茄鐮孢菌|Fusarium solani}}<ref name=c>BHATTI H N；RASHID M H；NAWAZ R，et al.Purification and characterization of a novel glucoamylase from Fusarium solani.Food Chemistry.2007，103（2）：338－43.</ref>、蔗草鐮刀菌 (Fusarium scirpi) <ref name=c/>及串珠鐮刀菌 (Fusarium moniliforme) <ref>{{cite journal |last1=Figueira |first1=Edson Luiz Zangrando |last2=Hirooka |first2=Elisa Yoko |title=Culture medium for amylase production by toxigenic fungi |journal=Brazilian Archives of Biology and Technology |date=2000 |volume=43 |issue=5 |pages=461–67 |doi=10.1590/S1516-89132000000500003 |accessdate=2019-12-24}}</ref>等，故而不同來源的[[酶|酶]]的性質也存在着差異。[[銅|銅]]離子及[[鎂|鎂]]離子等二價金屬離子一般對葡萄糖澱粉酶的活性有激活作用，然而[[汞|汞]]離子、[[鉛|鉛]]離子及[[鎳|鎳]]離子等二價金屬[[離子|離子]]對葡萄糖澱粉酶的活性有抑制作用，視乎葡萄糖澱粉酶的來源<ref name=a/>。

